;<16-BIT ADDITION CONSIDIRING CARRY>
 MVI C , 00H ;COUNTER REGISTER C
LHLD 2000H ;LOAD DATA FROM 2000H TO HL PAIR 1615
XCHG; EXCHNAGE HL-DE PAIR 
LHLD 2002H;LOAD DATA FROM 2002H TO HL PAIR 2010
DAD D; ADD HL AND DE  AND STORE IN HL
JNC NOC ;JUMP NOT CARRY
INR C ;INCREMENT COUNTER REGISTER
NOC: SHLD 2004H;;STORE IN 2004 REGISTER PAIR
MOV A,C ;MOVE C TO A 
STA 2006 ;STORE CARRY IN 2006 REGISTER
hlt